<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="arial">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Please accept this email as confirmation that </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">we have applied the discounted premium to your account</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><i><br>(Delete as required) </i></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">To confirm, </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">our underwriters have agreed to credit your credit card/debit card account with a payment of £0.00</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> which you can expect to receive in the next 3 to 5 working days. This is the </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">equivalent of 60 days’ worth of your base premium</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> (excluding any add-ons).<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><i>(Delete as required) </i></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">To confirm, </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">our underwriters have agreed to credit your bank account with a payment of £0.00 to your bank account</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">, which you can expect to receive in the next 3 to 5 working days. This is the </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">equivalent of 60 days’ worth of your base premium</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> (excluding any legal expenses and/or cyber liability add-ons). Please note that your payment schedule with Close Brothers will continue as planned,</span><b style="font-size: 12pt;"> this credit is intended to help cover instalments for the next two months</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>If you require further support, Close Brothers have a one-month payment holiday scheme in place. If you wish to apply for a one month payment holiday, you will need to contact Close Brothers on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">0333 321 8566 (Option 1)</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> or via this link: </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">https://d2cjxhvv9uqb7.cloudfront.net/</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">. Close Brothers will advise what the next steps are, but if you do have any problems in the meantime, please do not hesitate to contact us on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">01242 808 740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Please contact us if you have any further queries.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Customer Accounts Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>